<body>
    <div id='main'>
        <h1>Detailed !live help</h1>
        <h2>!LIVE LIST</h2>
            <p><b>!live list [(none)/featured/subscribed/live]</b> - Use no options to list all the streams that have been added. Use "featured" to list featured streams. Use "subscribed" to see your own subscribed streams. Use "live" to list all streams that are currently live.</p>
        <h2>!LIVE ADD/DEL</h2>
        <p><b>!live [add/del] URL</b> - Adds or removes a stream from the master list. Please be considerate when removing items.</p>
        <h2>!LIVE [UN]SUBSCRIBE</h2>
        <p><b>!live [un]subscribe URL</b> - Adds or removes a personal stream subscription. When you subscribe to a stream, the bot will private message you when the stream goes live.</p>
        <h2>!LIVE [UN]ALIAS</h2>
        <p><b>!live [un]alias URL [alias]</b> - Adds or removes a custom alias from any stream. Useful when, a user's name is not the same as their channel name.</p>
        <h2>!LIVE [UN]NSFW</h2>
        <p><b>!live [un]NSFW URL</b> - Adds or removes a NSFW warning for any stream. Useful for services (like livestream) who do not report the NSFW status of streams or for channels that are marked incorrectly. </p>
    </div>
